data.description: Seller offering $5000 towards closing costs!!!Welcome to your own piece of paradise on the serene Bayou Teche. This delightful 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom cottage offers a unique blend of modern convenience and rustic charm, all nestled on nearly an acre of picturesque land within the sought-after Cecilia school district. Bright and cozy is the theme for this home with a large wood buring fireplace being the centerpiece of the living space. The kitchen is bright and open with an expansive island perfect for entertaining. You'll find a convenient office nook between the kitchen and dining room perfect for homework or those days when you need to work from home. The generously sized primary suite is a true retreat, offering a peaceful haven after a long day. This property comes with a spacious shop, perfect for those who enjoy DIY projects, woodworking, or need additional storage space. The shop is a versatile area for a variety of hobbies and interests. Step outside onto the expansive covered porch and soak in the breathtaking views of the Bayou Teche. This is an ideal spot for sipping your morning coffee, watching the sunset, or hosting gatherings with family and friends. Contact your Realtor for an appointment before it's gone!
